<collectionCode id="ED37AE07CA40FFAFCC513619F9ECF5B6" box="[1588,1642,2577,2602]" pageId="16" pageNumber="635">IUCN</collectionCode>
(2008), Lekagul &amp; McNeeley (1991), Long (1992), Long &amp; Killingley (1983), Neal &amp; Cheeseman (1996), Pocock (1941a), Riffel (1991), Wozencraft (2005).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
